Description: For sale I have a 2006 Yamaha RGX121Z electric guitar in a sparkly Metallic Burgundy color. This guitar is a great player with powerful humbuckers with a good single coil pickup in the middle giving lots of sound options. The ohms on the 2 humbuckers both measure close to 12.5. Ohms on th single coil measure 5.75. The frets have just a few wear spots on the first three frets that don’t affect play. Electronics work as they should with a 5 position switch. The harmonics are ringing nicely and sustain is excellent. Tuners work smoothly and the guitar stays in tune. I feel it plays and sounds good enough to perform with the way it is, a very good Yamaha.... This is a used guitar that has nicks, dings, scuffs, and scratches but still presents nicely.
